{"tid":1694184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 星洲開藍絲大會 華記中伏失蹤 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-11-05T04:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:24:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c42e36e52bf847c7b897090b8e9ce6f81840fd0d","tid":1694184,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191105/U54E6LSFNQR7W2LCMSGSMXOHAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191105%2FU54E6LSFNQR7W2LCMSGSMXOHAM%2F&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=4243b2c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191105%2FU54E6LSFNQR7W2LCMSGSMXOHAM%2F&h=4e77cc3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191105/U54E6LSFNQR7W2LCMSGSMXOHAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n星洲開藍絲大會 華記中伏失蹤 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191105/large/1572884679_11a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191105%2Flarge%2F1572884679_11a4.jpg&h=d05aa8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nauthor<br />\n專欄作家 : 李八方<br />\n<br />\n藍絲KOL中，喺日本搞茶餐廳嘅華記楊官華算係惹火人物，佢之前已經成日俾黃絲鬧佢言論老屈，但華記一於少理，仲俾班藍絲係咁吹捧，搞到佢當正自己係正義化身，不過日前網上傳出楊官華好似瀨嘢，隨時要坐監，而且佢出事嘅地方，仲係藍絲日夜吹捧嘅新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍絲引述「要一別數載」<br />\n<br />\n話說早前楊官華喺fb專頁「華記正能量」宣傳去咗新加坡，仲話喺當地一間食肆舉行聚會，歡迎新加坡朋友到場發表對「香港的暴動事件睇法」，但有網民發現，原來喺新加坡公開討論他國政治屬犯法，搞政治集會亦要申請，於是一齊用電郵去信新加坡政府告發楊官華。<br />\n<br />\n之後有人發現，由10月20日後楊官華fb冇更新，到近日又再發文同相，但似乎係舊相，到噚日有同楊官華友好藍絲發片，稱收到楊短訊，話自己喺新加坡有牢獄之苦，形容係「中伏」、「泥菩薩過江」、「可能要同大家一別數載」，即時引起網民瘋傳，猜測佢係咪俾新加坡拉咗，之後又有其他愛國KOL發文，聲稱確認楊官華身處新加坡，但係要處理一啲問題，又話案件徹查當中，由於到𠵱家未見楊官華現身，好多網民相信佢真係於新加坡瀨嘢，有人仲話要召喚小鳳姐！<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"71a9a323d4d9620253062d823df726072c628afc","tid":1694184,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"華記無能源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0dd5c7bb5f4e7794753685d3ccacc11521726d","tid":1694184,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華記無能<span style=\"color: red;\">量</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22029c169a68053d004e192c6927eba0c3f97769","tid":1694184,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"去中国定坡狗到討論香港點樣革命安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c8b8c87a897ad18fb117e6bdeba1b107e3277b","tid":1694184,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"藍屍：可惡 乜新加坡冇自由架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1b3a6cb50c989ad41c9f91b869a5d20fad120b","tid":1694184,"uid":145326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"楊官華（缺能量）"},{"pid":"729c05d45de43a3faa95c49045cc606e34525790","tid":1694184,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}